info.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 09 at 2:43AM PST until February 09 at 8:00AM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM PST THIS MORNING... * WHAT...Northeast winds 15 to 30 mph with gusts up to 45 mph. * WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Beaches, San Luis Obispo County Inland Central Coast and Santa Lucia Mountains. * WHEN...Until 8 AM PST this morning. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
